metadata.name: Eternity
metadata.description: Ever since I was a child, I have wanted to be an astronaut, but I don't think my dream will ever come true... I believe in people who do space because they explore important spaces for all humanity. The second collection, like the first, will be based on my feelings, symbols and hidden details. The astronaut is a very important and iconic figure to me, bringing significance, trust and dream fulfilment. The second astronaut, who runs through the grass, shows the hope that everyone around the world needs...
